║  The Ten Commandments  ║
╚════════════════════════╝

1. be nice
2. try to respect channel topics
3. don't spam
IV. don't bring over drama from other servers. if you have grievances, try working it out over DMs
5. when discussing custom car hardware, follow ISO 26262 (more on this rule to follow)
6. don't instigate fights
7. don't cross-post the same thing across multiple channels
8. this one goes without saying, but i'm saying it anyways - don't break the law
9. racism / homophobia / transphobia / sexism / all the other forms of discrimination will not be tolerated
10. #9 exceeds all other rules
10.1. we don't count over 10.
